<<.graph>> updates on-the-fly to //any// changes you make. It's kind of fun, actually.

* Play with some of these example settings below.
* Drag the tiddlers around above. Experience the physics.
* Also, you add and remove nodes and edges in the graph above using the buttons overlaid on the graph.

